    "subtitle": {
      "text": "The Wither Skeleton held the watch at the end of the last age. The scroll is what they wrote down before it ended."
    },
    "description": [
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "  CH.10 · THE LAST WATCH",
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "",
      "▸ The Last Watch scroll is the cursed age gate.",
      "  It unlocks specific Ch12 content that cannot",
      "  be accessed without it.",
      "  You get it from the same farm you run",
      "  to summon the Wither in the first place.",
      "  One farm. Two objectives. Build it properly.",
      "",
      "◈ WITHER SKELETON FARMING",
      "  └ Spawn location: Nether Fortress corridors",
      "    and bridge sections (NOT open Nether)",
      "  └ Drop: Wither Skeleton Skull (~2.5% base rate)",
      "    Looting III: raises to ~5.5% — mandatory",
      "  └ Coal: guaranteed. Farm for Blaze Cakes too.",
      "  └ Last Watch scroll: 8% drop rate",
      "    Drops alongside standard loot — same farm",
      "",
      "◈ FORTRESS FARM DESIGN",
      "  └ Light up all non-target corridors (prevents",
      "    skeletons spawning outside kill zone)",
      "  └ Spawning platform: 30+ blocks, slab-floored",
      "    (slabs prevent Blazes from spawning there)",
      "  └ Water funnel system: wash Wither Skeletons",
      "    into a 1-block kill chamber",
      "  └ Sword + Looting III: melee required for heads",
      "    (Looting does not apply to projectile kills)",
      "  └ Expected rate with farm: ~1 skull per 5 min",
      "",
      "◈ SKULL MATH",
      "  └ 3 skulls: one Wither summon",
      "  └ 9 skulls: three Wither summons (one per Ch10/11/12",
      "    progression milestone)",
      "  └ Farm 9 skulls now. Do not come back here.",
      "",
      "◈ SCROLL: The Last Watch",
      "  └ 8% drop from Wither Skeletons",
      "  └ Research time: 20 min",
      "  └ Unlocks: cursed age content gate,",
      "    Ch12 specific research pathways",
      "",
      "▸ They called it the Last Watch",
      "  because nobody believed there would be another.",
      "  The scroll proves them wrong.",
      "  You are the next watch.",
      "",
      "▶ Find The Last Watch scroll [check]",
      "▶ Collect 9 Wither Skeleton Skulls",
      "",
      "◇ 9 skulls takes ~45 minutes with a proper farm.",
      "  Build the farm right the first time.",
      "  You will also need this fortress for Blaze farming.",
      "  The fortresses share the same infrastructure."
